\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

core
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

) of higher refractive index (e.g.
 the core of an optical fiber) surrounded by a 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

cladding
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

